# ============================================================
# QUESKA - EXPEDIA API CONFIGURATION
# ============================================================
# 
# Expedia offers two main APIs for travel integration:
#
# 1. RAPID API (Hotels/Lodging)
#    - Direct booking capability
#    - Real-time inventory and pricing
#    - 750,000+ properties worldwide
#    - Full booking lifecycle management
#    - Apply: https://partner.expediagroup.com/en-us/join-us/rapid-api
#
# 2. XAP API (Flights, Cars, Activities, Packages)
#    - Affiliate/deep-link model
#    - Users complete booking on Expedia
#    - Commission-based revenue
#    - Apply: https://developers.expediagroup.com/xap-apis/api/start-guide/getting-started
#
# ============================================================

# === Expedia API Credentials ===
# Shared credentials used by both Rapid API and XAP API
EXPEDIA_API_KEY=your_expedia_api_key_here
EXPEDIA_API_SECRET=your_expedia_api_secret_here

# === Environment Setting ===
# Set to True when ready for production
# False = test.ean.com (sandbox)
# True = api.ean.com (production)
EXPEDIA_USE_PRODUCTION=false

# ============================================================
# RAPID API - HOTEL BOOKING FEATURES
# ============================================================
#
# Available Features:
# - Property availability search
# - Room rate shopping
# - Real-time pricing
# - Direct bookings
# - Booking management
# - Property content (images, descriptions, amenities)
# - Guest reviews
#
# API Endpoints:
# - GET /v3/properties/availability - Search properties
# - GET /v3/properties/content - Get property details
# - POST /v3/itineraries - Create booking
# - GET /v3/itineraries/{id} - Retrieve booking
# - DELETE /v3/itineraries/{id}/rooms/{room_id} - Cancel
#
# Authentication:
# - Signature-based: SHA512(api_key + api_secret + timestamp)
# - Passed in Authorization header
#
# ============================================================

# ============================================================
# XAP API - FLIGHTS, CARS, ACTIVITIES
# ============================================================
#
# Available Services:
# 
# FLIGHTS:
# - One-way and round-trip search
# - Multiple cabin classes
# - Deep links to Expedia for booking
#
# LODGING (Alternative to Rapid):
# - Hotel search and listings
# - Deep links for booking
#
# ACTIVITIES:
# - Tours and sightseeing
# - Attractions and tickets
# - Outdoor activities
#
# CAR RENTALS:
# - Pickup/dropoff search
# - Multiple vehicle classes
# - Multiple suppliers
#
# PACKAGES:
# - Flight + Hotel bundles
# - Savings vs separate booking
#
# ============================================================

